            "description": "Scrapes the **Slotted Sarva Darshan** block from the TIRUMALA UPDATES section of https://www.tirumala.org/ in real time using a Playwright headless Chromium browser.\n\nSource text on the website:\n```\nRunning Slot: 1 on 27-Feb-2026\nBalance tickets for 27-Feb-2026: 0\nNote: Live tickets status may vary...\n```\n\n**No database reads or writes** — this is a pure live scrape from TTD's website.\n\n**Response fields:**\n- `running_slot` — current slot number/code being called\n- `slot_date` — ISO date (YYYY-MM-DD)\n- `slot_date_display` — original TTD format (27-Feb-2026)\n- `balance_tickets` — remaining tickets available\n- `balance_date` / `balance_date_display` — date the balance applies to\n- `note` — full note text from TTD\n- `scraped_at` — ISO timestamp of when this was scraped\n\n**Note:** Takes ~5-10 seconds as Playwright loads a real browser."
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "200 OK — scraped successfully",
              "status": "OK",
              "code": 200,
              "originalRequest": {
                "method": "GET",
                "header": [],
                "url": { "raw": "{{baseUrl}}/api/ssd/scrape", "host": ["{{baseUrl}}"], "path": ["api", "ssd", "scrape"] }
              },
              "body": "{\n  \"success\": true,\n  \"data\": {\n    \"running_slot\": \"1\",\n    \"slot_date\": \"2026-02-27\",\n    \"slot_date_display\": \"27-Feb-2026\",\n    \"balance_tickets\": \"0\",\n    \"balance_date\": \"2026-02-27\",\n    \"balance_date_display\": \"27-Feb-2026\",\n    \"note\": \"Live tickets status may vary by the time pilgrim reaches physically at the counters. Pilgrims are waiting in the Q-line to take the SSD tokens. Tickets will be issued on first-come-first-service basis\",\n    \"raw_text\": \"Running Slot: 1 on 27-Feb-2026 Balance tickets for 27-Feb-2026: 0 Note: ...\",\n    \"scraped_at\": \"2026-02-27T05:30:00.000Z\"\n  }\n}"
